# using speech recognizer chatter bot tkinter, and pyttsx3
# i will create an application that allows for vocal conversations with chatterbot
# BASIC PSEUDO
# get users first statement from microphone
# turn into an audio file
# read audio file into string
# submit string to chatterbot
# get chatterbot response
# speak and display chatterbot response into window
# await user speech once submitted display string into window to confirm is correct before re submitting to chatterbot
# basic components
# chatter bot object that gets user strings and returns responses as strings
# a user input object that gets microphone data and turns into audio file
# a audio file handler that converts to a string and checks if it is correct
# a tkinter based main to handle all buttons and displays
# EXTRAS 
# choose between training datas and customize voices